leaving_soon.title: Leaving Soon!
leaving_soon.description: Catch 'em while you can — these great titles won't be around for long!

299577.title: American Psycho 2
299577.description: 15 years later, Patrick Bateman's only survivor becomes a teaching assistant to a professor as she develops her own murderous obsessions.

299583.title: The Darkest Hour
299583.description: In this tense apocalyptic thriller, five youths fight to survive after being stranded in Moscow during an alien attack.

300177.title: Still Waiting
300177.description: The employees of a restaurant facing tough competition do everything they can to keep the eatery open. Desperate times call for desperate measures.

300448.title: Death At A Funeral
300448.description: After the unexpected death of a British patriarch, the dead man’s secrets leave the rest of his family with comical complications.

300452.title: The Man In The Iron Mask
300452.description: Three former musketeers attempt to unseat the tyrannical King Louis XIV and replace him with his alleged (and imprisoned) long lost twin.

301814.title: The Pink Panther 2
301814.description: Inspector Clouseau is back! This time, he's teaming up with a squad of international detectives to stop a globe-trotting thief from striking again.

301939.title: River's Edge
301939.description: A group of teenagers are thrown into a moral spin when one of them murders his girlfriend and they must decide whether to help him or turn him in.

302245.title: Getting Even With Dad
302245.description: In this heart-warming family-friendly comedy, a clever kid attempts to reform his con man father by blackmailing him into spending time with him.

302327.title: Guns Of The Magnificent Seven
302327.description: A noble gunfighter recruits a team of the deadliest cowboys in the West to help him free a peasant leader from a notorious Mexican prison.

302495.title: Shaquille O'Neal Presents: All Star Comedy Jam - Live From Las Vegas
302495.description: Shaquille O'Neal presents some of stand-up's freshest talent, as they bring down the house in this high-energy night of comedy!

304767.title: Shaquille O'Neal Presents: All Star Comedy Jam - Orlando
304767.description: Funnyman Gary Owen hosts stand-up comedy's most talented and sought after comedians; Capone, Lil' Duval, Tony Roberts and Jay Pharoah.

306935.title: Lars and The Real Girl
306935.description: A delusional young man strikes up an unconventional relationship with a doll he finds on the Internet in this weird and warm comedy.

310126.title: College
310126.description: They're not in college yet, but three high school seniors unexpectedly find themselves with the wildest frat on their prospective school's campus.

312170.title: Charlie Bartlett
312170.description: A cheeky high schooler sells prescription drugs to the kids of his new school while offering pseudo-psychiatric advice from a bathroom stall.

312172.title: Copying Beethoven
312172.description: In the days before the first performance of his Ninth Symphony, Beethoven needs help with copying the manuscript, so a promising student of composition, Anna Holtz, is sent to assist him. During the next two years, the final ones of Beethoven's life, Anna provides assistance to the deaf, temperamental, ailing man. In return, he tutors her in composition and explains to her the ideas and principles of Romanticism. Pushed away by Beethoven's derision of her work, Anna ultimately returns to find him near death. As he dictates his final compositions to Anna, Beethoven finally acknowledges that she is now free to become the composer she was always meant to be.

312179.title: Get Shorty
312179.description: A gangster goes to Hollywood to collect a debt and becomes a big-time producer when he realizes the movie business runs a lot like the mob.

321124.title: House of the Rising Sun
321124.description: The chief suspect for a robbery and murder must uncover the truth about the crime and identify the real culprit before he is sent back to prison.

349284.title: American Ghost Hunter
349284.description: In this unbelievable documentary, a paranormal investigator makes his way to his hometown in Iowa to release his family from decades of ghostly bonds.

356526.title: Be Cool
356526.description: Chili Palmer turns to the world of rock stars, pop divas, and hip hop gangstas when a new idea for a movie leads him into the music business.

380523.title: Frankie & Alice
380523.description: Inspired by a true story, a '70s go-go dancer with multiple personality disorder begins seeing a psychotherapist in an attempt to regain stability.

385507.title: Empire State
385507.description: When two friends attempt to rob an armored car depository containing millions, they must elude a veteran NYPD detective and angry local crime bosses.

389515.title: Griffin and Phoenix
389515.description: A poignant romantic comedy about two people who face a seemingly insurmountable obstacle that may stand between them and a last chance at love.

400850.title: Meatballs
400850.description: In this classic comedy, camp counselor Tripper guides a collection of lovable campers and libidinous staff through the pleasures of a coed summer,

405450.title: Walking Tall: The Payback
405450.description: Nick returns home after his sheriff father’s death in a suspicious car accident and is left with no choice but to take justice into his own hands.

437414.title: Tucker & Dale vs. Evil
437414.description: A group of college kids mistake Tucker and Dale for killer hillbillies and, when one goes missing, the misconception grows—along with the body count.

439504.title: Cocaine Cowboys
439504.description: In the early '80s, a new business emerged in Miami, FL, that changed the face of the city forever. That business was cocaine smuggling.

441466.title: There Be Dragons
441466.description: Arising out of the horror of the Spanish Civil War, a candidate for canonization is investigated by a journalist who discovers his own estranged father had a deep, dark and devastating connection to the saint's life.

448411.title: Alpha and Omega
448411.description: Two wolves upset the social order when the Alpha daughter of the pack leader and a jovial Omega are captured, fall in love, and try to save their kin.

448663.title: Leaving Las Vegas
448663.description: Determined to end it all, a committed drinker picks Vegas as his last stop, but he finds comfort with a kind prostitute who needs help of her own.

448986.title: The Magnificent Seven Ride!
448986.description: After the murder of his wife, the leader of the original Seven recruits five tough convicts to help him rescue a group of women from vicious bandits.

460610.title: How to Train Your Husband
460610.description: A foster puppy offers new insights into marriage, for a self-help author whose relationship with her husband could use a little rewrite.

460882.title: Bko Bangkok Knockout
460882.description: A range of martial art disciplines are unleashed as  a group of fight club friends join forces and fight for their lives to rescue a kidnapped friend.

460961.title: Ass Backwards
460961.description: Two lovable losers embark on a mayhem-filled road trip back to their hometown to win the pageant crown they never got as young girls.

461203.title: Instructions Not Included
461203.description: An Acapulco playboy's life turns upside down when a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep, and he has to raise the child on his own.

462800.title: Enron: the Smartest Guys in the Room
462800.description: The rise and fall of Enron is the focus as executives got rich pretending the company was more profitable while lower-level employees lost everything.

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

466704.title: Jamesy Boy
466704.description: The true story of a teen, who goes from a street gang to a maximum security prison, and the convicted murderer who helps him turn his life around.

468855.title: Carla
468855.description: Still struggling with her family's rejection, a transgender sex worker must choose between the man she loves and completing her transition.

469821.title: Fear
469821.description: A teenage girl’s dream crush on an older man, whom even her family approves of, turns terrifying when he reveals he’s an obsessed, psychopath stalker.

471290.title: Crystal
471290.description: A promise to her dead mother is all that 10 year old Crystal has left. Will she break it to save herself, or keep it and be sold again? Nandar Pictures presents CRYSTAL, based on a true story and starring Trinity Rose Miller and Jason London.

472111.title: Line of Duty
472111.description: Childhood friends find themselves on opposite sides of the law, as a pair of FBI agents go undercover to bring down a criminal drug empire.

472182.title: Escape From Planet Earth
472182.description: When a heroic astronaut from a blue-alien planet gets trapped on notoriously dangerous Earth, his overly-cautious brother must rescue him.

475195.title: Tesla Declassified
475195.description: Over 60 years after groundbreaking inventor and engineer Nikola Tesla’s death, research shows the forces guiding him and the elite rule opposing him.

475199.title: Alien Messiah
475199.description: A documentary that explores scientific questions of aliens influencing the Bible, with shocking theories of  UFOs and aliens engineering humans.

475643.title: Stargate
475643.description: A historical expert and a military unit travel through a mysterious portal. They land in a bizarre world occupied by a dangerous and powerful being.

476769.title: UFO Chronicles: Area 51 Exposed
476769.description: Many have suspected that government site Area 51 has a connection to aliens. A former weatherman reveals his shocking experiences and unique insights.

478517.title: The Beguiled
478517.description: Clint Eastwood is torn between his love and his life in this tense drama about a wounded Union soldier sheltered by a girls’ academy in the South during the height of the Civil War.

480226.title: Gacy
480226.description: He appeared to be a model citizen, father, and husband. This film dives into the psyche of this serial killer, who murdered over thirty men and boys.

480257.title: Mayor of the Sunset Strip
480257.description: Rodney Bingenheimer has witnessed rock go from glitter to grunge. He’s worn many hats and known many famous faces. This is his incredible story.

485311.title: Social Media Apocalypse
485311.description: A fascinating look at the world of social media, its influence and consequences, and whether a sinister agenda eliminates any good it can cause.

486668.title: Ron White: A Little Unprofessional
486668.description: With cigar and scotch in hand, the comedian delivers over an hour of new material in this live performance at the Paramount Theater in Austin, TX.

487716.title: The Amateurs
487716.description: Residents of a small town follow a charismatic ne'er-do-well, when he is struck by a flash of dubious inspiration to make an adult porn film.

487952.title: Illuminata
487952.description: When a turn-of-the-20th-century theater troupe rejects their playwright’s new opus, a melodrama builds around an influential critic and a seductress.

488965.title: The Pink Panther
488965.description: In this remake, the bumbling Inspector Jacques Clouseau tries to solve the murder and theft of a famous soccer coach and his priceless diamond ring.

493901.title: Conspiracy Chronicles: 9/11, Aliens and the Illuminati
493901.description: This doc reveals a captivating theory about the frightening and unholy alliance that connects the Illuminati to an extraterrestrial race.

497304.title: Redacted
497304.description: Brian De Palma directed this war drama that follows the various stories of U.S. soldiers in Iraq as seen through different forms of camera footage.

499511.title: Man on Wire
499511.description: Philippe Petit, who walked an illegally rigged highwire between NYC’s twin towers in 1974, faces stupendous challenges for the sake of his daring art.

505992.title: Diggers
505992.description: Four working class friends come of age, struggling to maintain their small-town ways as clam diggers on the shores of Long Island in an era of change.

507612.title: Monster Hunt 2
507612.description: The exciting sequel follows the heroic Wuba after he parts ways with his human parents and seeks to restore peace within the monster world.

508022.title: Angry White Man
508022.description: When a disaster ruins his wedding, a southern-fried redneck with nothing to lose takes his buddy on a crazy road trip in hopes of meeting his idol.

508260.title: Longing Nights
508260.description: Four twenty-somethings, two men and two women, navigate the nightlife of Madrid, Spain as a way to bridge the erotic loneliness in their lives.

511132.title: I Am Happiness on Earth
511132.description: A film director with a drug problem enters a passionate relationship with a sensitive dancer, as he gets lost between the worlds of art and reality.

514562.title: Phil Hartman: Behind Closed Doors
514562.description: After eight seasons on 'Saturday Night Live,' everyone knew Phil Hartman's name but few knew him.

514566.title: George Michael's Lonely Life
514566.description: George Michael was a worldwide superstar, yet he died alone on Christmas Day 2016.

516186.title: Ancient Aliens and the New World Order
516186.description: Hear conspiratorial arguments for alien life on Earth, its influence on elite society throughout history and its implications for future generations.

516208.title: Alien Watchers: Ancient Gods
516208.description: Learn how stories of UFO sightings, alien abductions and out-of-body experiences are not a modern phenomenon, but can be traced back millennia.

516859.title: The Last Witch Hunter
516859.description: A fearless, immortal witch hunter ends up in a ferocious battle with supernatural enemies as he fights to save the human race from evil.

517906.title: Black Rock
517906.description: Old friends reunite for a girls' weekend on an island off the coast of Maine, but one wrong move turns their getaway into a deadly fight for survival.

520427.title: Out of Liberty
520427.description: In 1839 Missouri, a lawman is caught between wanted men awaiting their upcoming hearing and the locals’ increased drive to remove the prisoners.

523954.title: An Artificial Reality
523954.description: An Orwellian meditation to raise our awareness on the way religion, governments, and corporations control and surveil every aspect of our lives.

526882.title: Mermaid Isle
526882.description: Tales of a cursed, evil mermaid lurking in a small town lake are the stuff of urban legend until four friends find out the hard way that she’s real.

534015.title: The Choice
534015.description: A carefree bachelor and a medical student in her own committed relationship must make a choice of the heart in this heart-lifting romance drama.

534021.title: Stronger
534021.description: A man who was maimed by the Boston Marathon bombing, becoming a double amputee, helps police find the terrorists while trying to heal from trauma.

534023.title: Exposed
534023.description: While investigating the death of his partner, a cop finds proof of corruption within his police department and a troubled woman with a secret.

539642.title: Hunting Evil
539642.description: A broken man returning to society after serving time meets an enigmatic entity that promises him riches in exchange for his soul.

539646.title: Dead Walkers: Rise of the 4th Reich
539646.description: A search party in Romania uncovers a bizarre, scientific, occult training ground of neo-Nazis building an army straight from the depths of hell.

550824.title: The Hunger Games
550824.description: In a dystopian future, 16-year-old Katniss volunteers to take her younger sister’s place in a battle where children must fight to stay alive.

550826.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
550826.description: As Katniss and Peeta embark on their victory tour, President Snow plans an even deadlier new Hunger Games, which threatens the future of Panem.

550828.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 2
550828.description: The celebrated movie series reaches its epic climax, as the brave Katniss fights to liberate Panem's citizens in a final showdown with President Snow.

551255.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 1
551255.description: The franchise phenomenon continues, as Katniss, having survived The Hunger Games, rises with District 13 to battle the oppressive President Snow.

552826.title: Chabelo Y Pepito Contra Los Monstruos
552826.description: Se fueron de excursión con los scouts y, al separarse del grupo, llegan a dar con una misteriosa gruta plagada de criaturas aterradoras.

555948.title: Tyler Perry's Madea's Tough Love
555948.description: In her first animated adventure, Madea sets out to save the Moms Mabley Youth Center from being shut down by using her hilarious confrontation style.

557739.title: Moonwalkers
557739.description: Unable to find Stanley Kubrick, an unstable CIA agent gets a seedy rock band manager to help pull off the biggest con ever: staging the moon landing.

559759.description: A paralyzing flash of light and sound that comes every day at the same time begins to destroy the life of a New York City air traffic controller.

561366.title: Ancient Extraterrestrials: Aliens & UFOs Before the Dawn of Time
561366.description: A scientific and scholarly argument for ancient alien and UFO visits to our Earth during a time when man lived among his Gods as cited in the Bible.

566169.title: Silent Trigger
566169.description: When his covert mission goes wrong, a former Special Forces agent, working as an assassin for a secret government agency, becomes their prime target.

568390.title: Seaside
568390.description: Daphne’s new life with her boyfriend on the Oregon Coast in his family’s beach house starts to unravel with a visit from his dangerously obsessed ex.

576110.title: Norm of the North 2: Keys to the Kingdom
576110.description: On call to New York and the Arctic, Norm must clear his name for a crime he didn’t commit and then stop a company from stealing his kingdom’s ice.

577658.title: Brotherhood
577658.description: A family man tries to forget his troubled past, but old foes quickly bring him back into the world and lifestyle he worked so hard to overcome.

580530.title: Detroit
580530.description: This relevant, fact-based story, set in 1967’s Detroit riots, tracks a group of rogue cops, who respond to a call with vengeance instead of justice.

591420.title: A Perfect Getaway
591420.description: A romantic Hawaiian vacation turns deadly for two pairs of lovers, when a duo of murderers begins targeting tourists who cannot escape the island.

591434.title: Trespass
591434.description: When two firemen discover a map leading to a fortune abandoned in a tenement, they become the targets of a vicious gang, led by a notorious mobster.

594576.title: The Congress
594576.description: Considered past-her-prime in Hollywood, an out-of-work actress agrees to one last job that traps her in a digital reality where she’s forever young.

605420.title: Street Fighter
605420.description: Jean-Claude Van Damme leads this box-office smash, adapted from the videogame, about a commando and his street fighters out to stop an evil general.

607105.title: American Me
607105.description: Edward James Olmos stars as a powerful Folsom State prisoner who returns to society after running the game behind bars for 18 years.

607451.title: E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial
607451.description: A boy forms a special bond with a sweet and gifted alien from another planet. He tries to keep it a secret, but he needs help to keep the visitor safe.

612171.title: Daniel Isn't Real
612171.description: After surviving a violent family trauma, a college freshman develops an ill-fated coping mechanism that resurrects an imaginary childhood friend.

612739.title: The Last Sentinel
612739.description: An electronically-enhanced soldier teams up with a fearless rebel fighter in humanity’s last line of defense against a deadly drone police force.

614173.title: The Final 24: Tupac Shakur
614173.description: A breakdown of the final hours of Tupac Shakur, the iconic rapper whose massive popularity and past troubles brought him both fans and enemies.

614786.title: The Flock
614786.description: A public safety officer who manages sex offenders in hard-nosed ways has to find a missing girl while he’s training his new by-the-book replacement.

620779.title: Siberia
620779.description: After an American diamond merchant and his lover fall into a bad business deal in Russia, they must evade crossfire between the buyer and Feds.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

621766.title: Fisherman's Friends
621766.description: In this fact-based music comedy, a crew of salty fishermen in the Celtic nation of Cornwall get signed to Universal Records and hit the Top 10 charts.

628023.title: The Best Little Whorehouse in Texas
628023.description: This rousing musical portrays a sheriff and a madam, who band together to save the infamous Texas Chicken Ranch from a big-city TV crusader.

628970.title: Hellboy II: The Golden Army
628970.description: Hellboy and his crew of paranormal outcasts face off with forces of darkness in this imaginative adventure from visionary director Guillermo del Toro.

629889.title: Charley Varrick
629889.description: Walter Matthau plays a petty thief who knocks off a mob bank and soon finds that both the police and a hit man are chasing after him.

630869.title: Tales From the Hood 2
630869.description: A horror-comedy anthology revolving around the Black American experience of institutional racism, police brutality, mass incarceration, and more.

630921.title: The Last House on the Left
630921.description: After their daughter is raped and left for dead, a couple exact bloody revenge on the attackers who have unknowingly taken shelter at their home.

637827.title: Don Jon
637827.description: A Jersey guy addicted to porn meets a charming and beautiful woman whom he hopes to pursue a real relationship with, but his habits get in the way.

637929.title: Carlito's Way
637929.description: In 1975 NYC, a rehabilitated ex-con drug dealer determined to stay clean is tempted back into the life by an array of lowlifes and former associates.

638331.title: Cowboys & Aliens
638331.description: “Iron Man” director Jon Favreau directed this sci-fi Western with Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford squaring off against a massive intergalactic threat.

638893.title: Deliver Us From Eva
638893.description: The formidable Eva Dandridge is considered an angel by her sisters, but their men think she’s a devil. Can a new suave player win her heart?

639974.title: To Wong Foo, Thanks for Everything! Julie Newmar
639974.description: John Leguizamo, Wesley Snipes, and Patrick Swayze are triple threats in this road trip romp about three drag queens who get stranded in a small town.

640125.title: The Quake
640125.description: A man and his family have just survived a flood, and now must escape the center of an earthquake, where skyscrapers are crumbling around them.

640197.title: Cold Case Hammarskjöld
640197.description: A director and private investigator put the pieces together surrounding the mysterious death of Swedish economist and diplomat Dag Hammarskjöld.

643056.title: The Parts You Lose
643056.description: Wesley, a young boy in a small North Dakota town, saves an unconscious, bleeding man, who turns out to be a potentially dangerous fugitive.

647078.title: Tales From the Hood
647078.description: Three young thugs show up to an inner-city funeral parlor for a drug pickup and are treated to four tales of horror from its maniacal mortician.

651741.title: Xingu
651741.description: Three brothers set out on a mission throughout Brazil, and in the process befriend many indigenous tribes, sparking an idea to create a national park.

654016.title: Something New
654016.description: A workaholic accountant living in Los Angeles must decide between a predictable IBM (Ideal Black Man) and her free-spirited white landscaper.

655009.title: Role Models
655009.description: A destruction of property offense lands a pair of energy drink sales reps a community service sentence as unlikely mentors in a Big Brother program.

658730.title: Una
658730.description: A young woman confronts her adult lover from her childhood looking for closure, but the secrets of their past threaten to unravel his new life.

659846.title: Waiting...
659846.description: A group of young employees at a chain restaurant ponder their lives while dealing with annoying patrons and staving off boredom with antics.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

665462.title: Apollo 13
665462.description: A routine space flight becomes a desperate battle of survival in this breathtaking and true-story of adventure, courage, and faith.

667306.title: Unsheltered
667306.description: After seeking shelter from a vicious storm, five college students are reported missing. They escaped mother nature, but can they escape their deaths?

668282.title: The Wedding Date
668282.description: A story about the road to finding true love. Kat’s single-girl anxiety prompts her to hire a male escort to pose as her date at her sister’s wedding.

672442.title: Dredd
672442.description: The head of Mega City One’s elite police force becomes the city’s last hope when a sex worker-turned-drug dealer aims to take over the city.

672494.title: A Perfect Ending
672494.description: When straight and married Rebecca seeks out the services of a high-priced sex worker, the last thing she expected was that she’d fall in love.

672670.title: The Derby Stallion
672670.description: An alcoholic former horse trainer perceives a unique gift for horses in a fifteen-year-old boy and makes it possible for him to conceive his dream.

675608.title: Saban's Power Rangers
675608.description: Five ordinary teenagers must team together to become something extraordinary in order to save the world from being obliterated by an alien threat.

675915.title: 13 Fanboy
675915.description: An obsessed fan stalks his favorite actors from the Friday the 13th films and beyond, mirroring his idol, Jason Voorhees.

680184.title: Crypto (Sub Esp)
680184.description: Demoted back to his hometown in upstate New York, a Wall Street banker puts his family in danger when he investigates a tangled web of corruption.

680256.title: Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain
680256.description: A documentary following Kevin Hart's 2012 international standup comedy tour, which included performances in 80 cities around the globe.

682385.title: Twisted Minds
682385.description: A young woman’s life is forever changed when she becomes pregnant after being raped by a stranger she met online and is left to raise his child.

682797.title: Casper
682797.description: Seeing is believing in this adventure about a kind spirit in need of a friend and his ghostly uncles who want all “fleshies” out of their manor.

686278.title: Doom
686278.description: Based on the hit videogame, this adventure begins when a call for help from a research station on Mars sends a team of mercenary Marines into action.

689650.title: The Pink Panther
689650.description: The bumbling Inspector Jacques Clouseau tries to catch an infamous jewel thief before he can steal a priceless diamond from a princess.

694011.title: Vice
694011.description: This acclaimed biopic explores how Dick Cheney quietly wielded immense power as George W. Bush's Vice President, reshaping the U.S. and the globe.

694229.title: American Pie Presents: Band Camp
694229.description: Get ready for the antics when Stifler’s younger brother spends a summer encountering camp counselors, hidden cameras, and a pair of Playmates.

694233.title: American Pie Presents: The Book of Love
694233.description: With the help of the legendary Book of Love, three friends embark on an outrageous quest to lose their virginity with the girls of their dreams.

694577.title: American Reunion
694577.description: The whole American Pie gang returns to East Great Falls, Michigan to make their reunion into the most outrageous weekend since high school.

694581.title: American Pie Presents: Beta House
694581.description: Get ready for the most outrageous freshman year in collegiate history as Dwight Stifler, his cousin Erik, and Jim’s dad pledge a wild fraternity.

694621.title: Balls of Fury
694621.description: An action-packed comedy about a former professional table tennis player, Randy Daytona, who is recruited by the FBI for a secret mission.

694702.title: American Wedding
694702.description: When Jim and Michelle decide it's time to tie the knot, the gang celebrates this rite of passage with a wild bachelor party accompanied by Jim's dad.

694768.title: American Pie
694768.description: The stakes are high when four friends make the pact to lose their virginity by prom night in this romp about high school, band camp and apple pie.

695015.title: American Pie Presents: The Naked Mile
695015.description: Erik Stifler, his devoted friends and some uninhibited sorority girls take the chance of their lives at the annual and infamous Naked Mile race.

695341.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?
695341.description: Four couples on an annual retreat struggle to save their marriages while each of them battles their own financial, physical and emotional issues.

696058.title: American Pie 2
696058.description: A year after their prom night misadventures, the gang reunites for a summer they'll never forget at a beach house they turn into party central.

698792.title: Assault on Precinct 13
698792.description: Two men on opposite sides of the law join forces in an epic New Year's Eve battle against an enemy that doesn’t follow the code of cop or criminal.

698959.title: Repo Men
698959.description: After being outfitted with a top-of-the-line heart replacement, an organ repo man must go on the run when he finds himself unable to pay for it.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

698980.title: Dead Silence
698980.description: After the murder of his wife, a man returns to his hometown and uncovers the terrifying legend of Mary Shaw, a cursed ventriloquist from the 40s.

698981.title: Drag Me to Hell
698981.description: When loan officer Christine decides to evict an older woman, she becomes the victim of an evil spirit determined to drag her to hell.

698985.title: The Signal
698985.description: In this sci-fi thriller, three students encounter a mysterious signal in the desert and find themselves at the mercy of a man in a hazmat suit.

701042.title: Valentina's Wedding
701042.description: Families feud and laughs fly as a woman becomes torn between her perfect life and boyfriend in New York and her ex and a political dynasty in Mexico.

701770.title: Danger Close
701770.description: Major Harry Smith leads 108 novice soldiers into an impossible battle in Vietnam that challenges their courage to triumph against overwhelming odds.

706385.title: Bad Hurt
706385.description: A family’s triumphs and struggles shine through as they handle the dual issues of their son returning from war and caring for a disabled daughter.

706386.title: C.O.G.
